         <abstract id="aspace_bc0401186a11cbe0c8076e0404f0e053">Arthur Ware Locke was Professor of Music at Smith College from 1915 to 1952. His papers contain correspondence, compositions, publications, photographs, and news clippings documenting his work.</abstract>
      </did>
