      <scopecontent id="aspace_c54594e89ba92a83c46639dbe73313d7">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains photographs of Arthur Ware Locke teaching, news clippings about his career, compositions for various events at Smith College, and material related to his book, <title render="italic">Selected Lists of Choruses for Women's Voices</title>, including correspondence to publishers and co-author, Fassett manuscripts, and notes.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
